item.title: [+2718] The Sad Reality Behind Ronald McDonald (w/ PICS)
item.description: Ronald McDonald has long been an admired figure. Kids the world over brighten up when they see the affable clown, with his unmistakable red hair, yellow jumpsuit and striped shirt. But little does anyone know the true and sad story behind the clown. Wipe away the makeup and you'll find something not so pretty.

item.title: [+667] Washington Drug Agents Seize Pot Legalization Petitions
item.description: Marijuana advocacy group Sensible Washington, says it has learned that a dozen signed copies of the marijuana legalization initiative for Washington State of which it is the sponsor, were seized last week by the federally-funded WestNET drug task force.

item.title: [+644] Megan Fox: I wasn't fired—I QUIT Transformers 3!
item.description: Following the shocking report that she was dumped by director Michael Bay from the upcoming Transformers 3, Fox issued a statement to People magazine last night, saying that she actually left the movie and was not fired. "Megan Fox will not be starring in Transformers 3," her reps told the magazine.

item.title: [+638] Scientists Create The First Synthetic Cell
item.description: Heralding a new era in biology, scientists for the first time have created a synthetic cell, completely controlled by man-made genetic instructions, which can survive and reproduce itself.
